Ok then, plastic.

00:01:06.603 --> 00:01:09.943
Today we use plastic in just about everything.

00:01:10.443 --> 00:01:16.993
Toys, technology, cars, appliances and even building materials all contain plastic.

00:01:17.763 --> 00:01:22.353
The device you’re listening to this on is made possible thanks to plastic.

00:01:23.173 --> 00:01:28.683
Globally we produce over 380 million tonnes of plastic every year.

